Wash and cut Granny Smith apple into small pieces and place in a small bowl. Add lemon juice and toss. Set aside. In a large bowl mix the lettuce, raisins, walnuts, blue cheese crumbles, and green onion. Add the Granny Smith apple pieces and mix well. Toss with the Sweet Honey Dressing until coated. Garnish with dried apple slices, Serve immediately. To make the dressing: In a jar with a lid combine all ingredients. Shake dressing and pour over the salad.